title: La Mif
overview: Carla and Kévin invite you to their home, in Marseille, to discover their house, their daily life with the family and to make an update without wooden language: their long absence, their disappointments and sometimes even their beautiful surprises… Without detour, they reveal themselves like you've never seen them before! Accompanied by their crazy band of friends "La Mif" who are ready to do everything to help Carla and Kévin and complete the various missions that will be entrusted to them!
